Package org.gbif.mybatis.type

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EnumConverter<K,T extends Enum<?>>
    Generic enumeration value converter interface for mapping magic keys used for persisting to their respective enum values and vice versa.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseConverter<K,T extends Enum<?>>
    Generic converter class using an immutable bimap for mapping key/values.
    BaseEnumTypeHandler<K,T extends Enum<?>>
    Base handler for all Enums from the term_type table that are backed by the preferred terms of the term table.
    CountryConverter
    Enum converter for Country.
    CountryTypeHandler
    MyBatis TypeHandler for Country enum.
    EnumDictTypeHandler<T extends Enum<?>>
    General enumeration type handler that converts enums into their string name() representation and vice versa.
    LanguageConverter
    Enum converter for Language.
    LanguageTypeHandler
    MyBatis type handler for Language.
    StringArrayTypeHandler  
    UriArrayTypeHandler  
    UriTypeHandler
    A simple converter for varchars to URI.
    UuidTypeHandler
    Handler for UUID types.
